'''Master of Whisperers''' is an important position on the King's [[small council]] in the [[Seven Kingdoms]], the government of the realm. He advises the King on matters of espionage and state intelligence. In the first season this position is held by Lord [[Varys]] under King [[Robert Baratheon]]. Varys remains in the role under Robert's successors King [[Joffrey Baratheon|Joffrey]] and King [[Tommen Baratheon|Tommen]]. The current status of the position is unclear, as Varys decided to leave [[Westeros]] with [[Tyrion Lannister]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Children]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
